OL,3,CPrestigious theatre school attended by
OL,4,COlivia Colman scraps undergrad degrees
OL,6,FOne of the West Country's leading
OL,7,Ftheatre schools has scrapped its
OL,8,Fundergraduate degree courses due to
OL,9,F"unprecedented funding challenges".
OL,11,FThe Bristol Old Vic Theatre School -
OL,12,Fwhose alumni include Oscar winners
OL,13,FOlivia Colman and Sir Daniel Day-Lewis
OL,14,F- will no longer accept undergraduate
OL,15,Fstudents from September this year.
OL,17,FOther notable stars who were taught at
OL,18,Fthe school, which first opened in
OL,19,F1946, include Sir Patrick Stewart,
OL,20,FJeremy Irons, Gene Wilder, Naomie
OL,21,FHarris and Miranda Richardson.
