OL,6,FSenior staff said the decision was
OL,7,Fmade with the "students' best
OL,8,Finterests at heart".
OL,10,FFiona Francombe, Principal and CEO of
OL,11,FBristol Old Vic Theatre School, said:
OL,12,F"Along with many Arts and Higher
OL,13,FEducation organisations, we are facing
OL,14,Funprecedented funding challenges which
OL,15,Fwe need to address as our current
OL,16,Ftraining model, focusing on teaching
OL,17,Fundergraduate degree courses, is not
OL,18,Fviable in the future.
