OL,6,F"As a result, we will no longer be
OL,7,Foffering undergraduate training from
OL,8,FSeptember but will continue to provide
OL,9,Fpostgraduate training and other
OL,10,Fcourses.
OL,12,F"By taking this decision now, we are
OL,13,Fable to plan for the next two academic
OL,14,Fyears calmly, and with our students'
OL,15,Fbest interests at heart.
