OL,3,CPrestigious theatre school attended by
OL,4,COlivia Colman scraps undergrad degrees
OL,6,F"It is our intention to create a long-
OL,7,Fterm sustainable future for the school
OL,8,Fwhere we can deliver high calibre
OL,9,Ftraining for which the school is
OL,10,Frenowned but we need time and space to
OL,11,Fwork through the options and our
OL,12,Fcurrent focus must be on existing
OL,13,Fstudents and staff."
OL,15,FCurrent undergraduates will be allowed
OL,16,Fto complete their studies, while the
OL,17,Fschool will continue to offer
OL,18,Fpostgraduate courses in acting,
OL,19,Fwriting, directing and performance
OL,20,Fdesign.
